Write a program to scan the string from the user and to print it.

Input Format:

Input consist of 1 string.
Sample Input & Output:

Hello

The string is Hello

import java.util.Scanner;
public class Main
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        //Write your code
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        //getting user input
        String text = sc.next();
        //display user input
        System.out.println("The string is "+text);
        
    }

Write a program to scan the string from the user and to print it.

Input Format:

Input consist of 1 string.
Sample Input & Output:

Hello World

The string is Hello World

import java.util.Scanner;
public class Main
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        //declare scanner class
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        //get user input
        String text = sc.nextLine();
        //display user input
        System.out.println("The string is "+text);
    }
}
